info_2 <- info_1 |> 
  provider:::gt_prov(source = "Source: NPPES NPI Public Registry.", 
                     checkmark = c("sole_proprietor")) |> 
  gt::tab_header(title = paste0("General Information for: ", 
                                info_1$first_name, " ", 
                                info_1$middle_name, ". ", 
                                info_1$last_name, ", ",
